<li id="cite_note-84"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-84">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">see e.g. <a href="#CITEREFAvari2007">Avari 2007</a>, p.&#160;77 <a href="/wiki/Max_M%C3%BCller" title="Max Müller">Max Müller</a> gave 1700–1100 BCE, <a href="/wiki/Michael_Witzel" title="Michael Witzel">Michael Witzel</a> gives 1450–1350 BCE as <i>terminus ad quem</i>.</span>
